summary:
For nearly 20 years I have been active in export of installations and equipment to East- and Central-Europe. My activities did consist of: aquisition, sales and realisation of (large) turnkey projects. Project sums were in the range from € 0,5 mln up to € 10 mln. 

Experience:
- experienced traveller, I have been travelling to both cities and rural areas all over the world 
 (business & private);
- provide functional leadership to 4-5 employees; 
- to provide full guidance for foreign prospects / clients during their visits to The Netherlands;
- arranging shipments abroad by curtainsider trucks or containers (in range from 1 to 160 TUE);
- working with confirmed Letters of Credit and structured trade financing;
- project management for greenhouse-construction projects;
- working with interpreters and translators;
- working out detailed technical quotations (in range from 1 to 160 pages);
- working out detailed commercial contracts;
- prepare extensive applications for horticultural tenders (in range from € 1 mln. to € 10 mln.).
